### 4. Get all customers (page 0, size 10) - ADMIN ONLY
# Replace YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN with the token from step 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 5. Get customers with search (search by name)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=0&size=10&search=Carl
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 6. Get customers filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=0&size=10&status=active
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 7. Get customers with search and status filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=0&size=10&search=Robert&status=active
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 8. Get customers sorted by name ascending
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=0&size=10&sortBy=name&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 9. Get customers page 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

